<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Timbered" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Timbered,</orth> built, framed, shaped: <cit><quote>my arrows, too slightly t. for so loud a wind, would have reverted,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his bark is stoutly t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 48</bibl></cit>.
